Glass blowing home studio gear for sale.  Includes most of the things you need to get started flame working glass.  Fume hood, extractor fan, kiln, sandblaster, compressor, wet saw, rollers, bench, backsplash, Homefill oxygen system, oxygen tank, Bethlehem Bravo torch, electric footpedal, marver, hoses and regulators.  Just add tools and your ready to go.  Clear glass and a box of short color is included.  Tube 75, 50, 44, 38 25, 20, 16, 12, 10.  Rod. 14, 12, 10, 8, 7, 6, 5, 3
